code: "use strict";export const isPlainObject=value=>{if(typeof value==='object'&&value!==null){return Object.getPrototypeOf(value)===Object.prototype;}return false;};export const deepFreeze=object=>{if(true){return object;}if(Object.isFrozen(object)){return object;}if(!isPlainObject(object)&&!Array.isArray(object)){return object;}for(const key in object){if(key!=='params'){if(Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptor(object,key)?.configurable){const value=object[key];deepFreeze(value);}}}return Object.freeze(object);};
